Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.82,0:00:14.82,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,There are some\Nlacerations to your stomatitis.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.13,0:00:15.80,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.29,0:00:19.83,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,...a little soot is\Nstuck to your bronchus.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.90,0:00:21.87,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,Please rest quietly in\Nbed for a couple of days...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.93,0:00:22.88,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,I don't have time!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.93,0:00:23.91,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,Leave!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.14,0:00:28.91,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,You guys couldn't\Neven kill the Orange Girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.24,0:00:30.45,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,Shame on you!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.91,0:00:34.01,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,Your job is to deal with\Nthis type of thing, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.48,0:00:36.65,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,You made it easy for\Nthem to kidnap my dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.78,0:00:38.92,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,Are you guys really macho men?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.98,0:00:40.02,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,Useless!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.89,0:00:42.66,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,Ms. Momomi...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.72,0:00:43.49,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.59,0:00:46.43,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,Can I borrow this?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.86,0:00:47.53,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.37,0:01:00.51,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,What happened to Hirooka?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.70,0:01:02.91,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,He went to the district police station.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.97,0:01:06.08,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,He's making sure the\NOwner's kidnapping doesn't get out.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.44,0:01:10.22,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,Find the kidnappers and get\Nmy dad back, as soon as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.71,0:01:13.72,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,Get pictures of their faces simulated\Nfrom my and Hirooka's memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.75,0:01:14.92,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,I want their faces!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.39,0:01:18.39,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,You can leave now.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.99,0:01:21.09,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,But, this one's still breathing.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.80,0:01:37.18,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,This is more work than I thought...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.61,0:01:38.64,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,Mikura.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.08,0:01:41.18,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,Cheer up and give us a hand here!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.51,0:01:44.08,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,Let's do my plan instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.15,0:01:44.75,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.25,0:01:49.96,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,We have to bury him and\Ndisappear from town soon...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.15,0:01:53.10,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,otherwise we'll\Ndisappear from life instead!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.72,0:01:56.83,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,You hit Momoi's daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.29,0:01:59.17,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,When she was seven years old...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.23,0:02:01.57,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,...she decided that the color of blood...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.90,0:02:04.11,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,...was a symbol of youth,\Nand killed dozens of people.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.37,0:02:06.71,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,Damn psycho bitch!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.87,0:02:10.58,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,Moreover, she is respected for her\Ncharm and cleverness by everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.87,0:02:14.65,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,Also, she uses her influence over\Nbig businesses to cover up her crimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.28,0:02:18.62,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,What can we do to people like her?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.85,0:02:19.59,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,No problem!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.22,0:02:23.03,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,They haven't realized Momoi's dead...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.12,0:02:24.50,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,...so we can use that!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.69,0:02:30.26,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,They can't be careless with us...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.63,0:02:32.80,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,We're worse than they are!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.50,0:02:35.34,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,She knows nothing of the world...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.93,0:02:38.17,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,Or she is fearless...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.87,0:02:40.51,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,She doesn't get it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.91,0:02:45.08,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,Then I'll quit this job.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.31,0:02:47.25,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,I won't see you guys again!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.71,0:02:49.05,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,Mikura...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.18,0:02:52.63,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,Don't you think we should\Nbury him somewhere else?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.55,0:02:55.69,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,Back off, Old Man.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.23,0:03:04.83,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,Sorry, to have to do that...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.89,0:03:07.84,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,...I didn't think you guys would\Nbe willing to listen to my story.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.30,0:03:09.74,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,I-I-I'll listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.80,0:03:12.11,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,Digging this hole isn't that\Nimportant, right, Mr. Kuro?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.34,0:03:14.68,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,We're we digging our own grave?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.74,0:03:16.88,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,Let me listen to everything, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.04,0:03:18.21,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,Right, Mikura?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.68,0:03:20.21,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,Old Man, who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.31,0:03:21.85,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,Let's listen to him, Mikura.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.28,0:03:26.42,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,I'm a hit man who was\Nhired by Momoi, a while ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.52,0:03:28.22,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,Hit man?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.26,0:03:35.96,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,Mezzo!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.73,0:03:37.64,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,Mezzo?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.10,0:03:41.84,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,But, isn't this too out in the open?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.93,0:03:43.91,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,Are you sure this is the\Nbest place to bury him?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.97,0:03:46.34,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,Not even Colombo would find this.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.40,0:03:49.21,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,Maybe it's the best place for Momoi.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.21,0:03:56.49,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,I was fed up with\Neating noodles, every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.58,0:04:00.86,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,It's good!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.02,0:04:03.26,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,I'll eat a lot because\NI'm a growing child, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.52,0:04:04.26,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,Yes, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.32,0:04:06.27,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, just please, eat up.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.79,0:04:10.70,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,Do you all remember the\NBloody Pennant Race Case?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.93,0:04:11.91,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.10,0:04:15.91,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,Four batters of pro baseball teams\Nwere found dead, gunned down...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.97,0:04:18.61,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,A serial murder case\Nthat was never solved.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.27,0:04:22.84,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,I was a green officer,\Nso I investigated passionately.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.64,0:04:27.05,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,Back then, you must have been a\Nyoung man with a strong sense of justice!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.08,0:04:29.75,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,I bet you had a lot of hair, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.08,0:04:31.08,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,Long hair.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.41,0:04:33.09,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,I hit on all the girls!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.28,0:04:34.78,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,Bad news!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.02,0:04:37.22,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,It was fashionable then.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.52,0:04:40.83,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,At headquarters, we were sure it\Nwas a plot by one of the other teams...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.19,0:04:45.26,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,...however, we could never find\Nany suspects or physical evidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.60,0:04:47.60,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,I did it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.86,0:04:49.64,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,Momoi ordered me to.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.53,0:04:53.17,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,You're good, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.64,0:04:56.74,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,Half a year ago, I retired...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.07,0:04:59.45,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,Momoi didn't accept it, did he?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.51,0:05:00.11,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,That's not it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.18,0:05:04.59,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,He expressed his appreciation for my\Nefforts and gave plenty of parting gifts.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.15,0:05:07.69,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,You're loaded then, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.25,0:05:11.70,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,The problem was Momoi's daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.02,0:05:13.56,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,That psycho bitch!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.99,0:05:18.53,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,She has a very suspicious nature\Nand thought I'd betray the organization.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.59,0:05:20.16,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,She tried to kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.23,0:05:21.44,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,Yes, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.53,0:05:23.60,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,That's why you asked us to kidnap him?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.67,0:05:27.34,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,I wanted to use him as insurance\Nuntil I escaped overseas...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.40,0:05:29.38,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,But now, he's dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.47,0:05:30.88,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,Isn't it Heaven's judgment?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.94,0:05:32.82,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,He's responsible for so many crimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.04,0:05:35.72,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,But it's not what I asked for.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.78,0:05:37.59,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,Then what do you want us to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.28,0:05:41.59,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,Please carry out Mikura's plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.88,0:05:43.09,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.15,0:05:44.26,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,Lucky!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.49,0:05:48.37,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,If we don't, we'll be\Nkilled by the psycho bitch.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.42,0:05:49.13,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,However, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.19,0:05:50.30,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,Well, Harada?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.43,0:05:51.93,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,It's adding fuel to the flames.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.03,0:05:56.20,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,Pops, this is a good chance to\Nsmash in that psycho bitch's face!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.40,0:05:57.61,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,Right, Harada?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.67,0:05:59.34,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,We can do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.64,0:06:01.64,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,If we don't, you'll kill us, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.70,0:06:03.68,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,Except Mikura.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.74,0:06:04.27,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.74,0:06:07.22,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,Because Mikura and I\Nhave the same opinions.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.28,0:06:08.69,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.01,0:06:13.15,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,It's impossible for this\Nold man and I to do it alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.15,0:06:15.69,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,We didn't order these.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.52,0:06:18.86,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,They're from the two\Ncustomers over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.86,0:06:25.10,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,You guys!\NThe fat pervert?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.83,0:06:29.04,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,I didn't think we'd run into you again...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.23,0:06:30.77,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,We're out of luck...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.97,0:06:32.61,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.37,0:06:35.28,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,W-What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.01,0:06:43.39,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,Did you come to pay your bill?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.85,0:06:46.22,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,I'll pay for your burial.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.72,0:06:49.13,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,If I ever see your dirty faces again...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.29,0:06:50.73,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,I won't go easy on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.89,0:06:51.76,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.52,0:06:53.26,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.32,0:06:54.63,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,Look, a naked woman!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.69,0:06:55.66,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,No shit!\NWhere is she?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.66,0:06:56.46,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,Where is she?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.73,0:07:00.73,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,And I didn't even have\Ntime to eat my Sunday!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.83,0:07:01.40,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,Bastards!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.63,0:07:02.58,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,That's gotta hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.67,0:07:08.91,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,Those two will cover our tab.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.61,0:07:14.68,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,Where did the old man go?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.94,0:07:17.19,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,Mr. Kuro, what\Nshould we do now?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.78,0:07:20.42,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,We were only warming up, right...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.78,0:07:21.69,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,Pops?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.76,0:07:34.30,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,Who is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.03,0:07:40.21,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,What kind of idiotic daredevil...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.34,0:07:42.51,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,...would try to sneak into my room?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.14,0:07:45.59,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,Even if I was\Nsleeping with a tranquilizer...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.78,0:07:47.22,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,So, what is your plan now?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.18,0:07:52.12,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,Papa?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.68,0:07:53.96,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,Were you able to run away?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.02,0:07:54.69,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,Were you hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.75,0:07:55.96,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.15,0:07:58.29,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,I want to show you something.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.46,0:08:02.09,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,You!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.73,0:08:05.04,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,You two must get along.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.16,0:08:06.73,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about, Papa?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.96,0:08:09.47,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,She is the Orange Girl\Nwho kidnapped you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.00,0:08:11.77,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,Calm down, Momomi.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.44,0:08:14.24,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,Don't you think we look alike?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.45,0:08:26.05,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,Don't you think we look alike?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.78,0:08:29.42,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.75,0:08:31.06,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,Ms. Momomi, please...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.55,0:08:33.33,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,...come to Room G immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.02,0:08:35.87,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,"This is a hand made ransom note..."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.93,0:08:37.30,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,"Read carefully."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.46,0:08:43.78,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,"We'll exchange Momokichi's life\Nfor 3 hundred 97 million yen."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.70,0:08:49.38,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,"We'll contact you with the\Nplace and time three days from now."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.51,0:08:51.85,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,"The psycho bitch makes the deal."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.01,0:08:56.35,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,"Open parenthesis, Momomi,\Nthat means you, close parenthesis."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.25,0:09:00.35,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,"You have to come by yourself..."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.52,0:09:02.93,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,"Please look at the enclosed disk, too."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.09,0:09:05.86,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,"Don't play petty tricks."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.39,0:09:08.70,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,"From the Orange Girl and friends."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.49,0:09:11.47,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,Show me the disk.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.66,0:09:12.26,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.83,0:09:17.74,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,Look at the central monitor, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.77,0:09:22.61,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,Papa!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.67,0:09:23.38,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,The Owner!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.01,0:09:26.15,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,Momomi, don't resist them.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.88,0:09:30.98,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,I've never seen such\Nstrong and terrible people.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.88,0:09:33.12,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,Terrible...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.82,0:09:37.92,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,I can't believe it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.29,0:09:42.24,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,I can easily see his mental\Nand physical exhaustion.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.66,0:09:44.07,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,We should accept the deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.59,0:09:47.77,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,You think I'll pay the ransom?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.76,0:09:51.80,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,Then will you leave\Nthe Owner stranded?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.90,0:09:55.44,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,We have three days\Nuntil they'll contact us.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.57,0:09:56.95,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,We'll stall them.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.27,0:10:00.72,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,They won't kill Papa\Nuntil they'll get the money.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.08,0:10:04.82,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,But, can we recapture\Nhim in such a short time?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.25,0:10:07.45,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,We don't even know who they are.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.15,0:10:11.06,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,They must have\Nthings to hide, so access the...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.22,0:10:16.33,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,...personal data of the district police\Nstation and run their faces through it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.03,0:10:20.53,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,If they have a criminal\Nhistory, it'll be very easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.00,0:10:23.60,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,Ms. Momomi, we\Nsimulated their pictures.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.80,0:10:30.15,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,Oh, I'm so hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.57,0:10:32.58,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,We still have plenty to eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.68,0:10:33.85,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,Want Tonkotu Ramen?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.91,0:10:37.29,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,Why do we only have noodles?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.55,0:10:40.43,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,I'm tired of instant noodles...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.72,0:10:44.13,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,I'm tired too, because\NI've been up all night...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.32,0:10:45.89,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,Don't complain.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.43,0:10:50.77,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,Let me go shopping.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.43,0:10:53.37,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,The supermarket is right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.83,0:10:56.67,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,Mr. Kuro prohibited us from going out.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.20,0:11:00.67,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,He said don't walk around\Nuntil the deal is done with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.10,0:11:02.95,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,You worry too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.31,0:11:06.01,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,We don't need to worry\Nbecause we have a hostage.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.34,0:11:06.98,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,I'll go.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.38,0:11:08.65,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,Hey, Mikura!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.88,0:11:11.69,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,They're desperate, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.75,0:11:13.39,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,If something happens to you...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.98,0:11:16.16,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,Do you think they can kill me?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.47,0:11:40.35,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,Make it short because\NI'm expected back any second.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.28,0:11:43.85,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,You made it on time.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.98,0:11:46.86,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,The other two didn't find out?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.18,0:11:52.16,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,If you're plotting something\Nbad, you won't live past dinner!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.52,0:11:56.03,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,I want to give you something.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.16,0:11:57.73,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,Can you come with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.97,0:12:10.45,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,Please take care of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.44,0:12:15.18,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry about last time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.31,0:12:16.92,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,Is your ear okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.45,0:12:18.89,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,Keep the promise...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.18,0:12:21.22,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,The relationship\Nbetween you and the chief...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.25,0:12:24.29,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,I'll keep it only in my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.35,0:12:25.39,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,Promise me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.52,0:12:27.97,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,Don't write about it in the next volume!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.06,0:12:28.97,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.02,0:12:30.37,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,I can't concentrate, stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.53,0:12:32.23,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,Shut it, I'm a real detective!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.29,0:12:33.07,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,Jerk!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.91,0:12:51.29,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,Where is the Owner?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.41,0:12:52.95,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,How did you find us already?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.22,0:12:56.82,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,We met some helpful collaborators.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.72,0:12:59.36,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,Tell me where the Owner is.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.56,0:13:02.70,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,Do you think I'll tell you so quickly?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.63,0:13:04.46,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,Ouch...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.53,0:13:05.04,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,O-Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.09,0:13:06.57,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,I don't like pain!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.66,0:13:08.64,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,O-Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.20,0:13:16.15,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,Human willpower is so very fragile...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.34,0:13:18.25,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,Should I pry off your nose next?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.31,0:13:20.98,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,I'll tell you, I'll tell you...\NI'll tell you everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.48,0:13:26.26,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,Trash detectives who get fired shouldn't\Ntry to increase their income so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.95,0:13:27.98,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,That's true...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.35,0:13:31.09,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,Son of a...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.66,0:13:34.63,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,Screw you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.52,0:13:39.13,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,Not so bad for a trash detective, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.10,0:13:40.87,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.10,0:13:44.10,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,If you tell me where\Nthe Owner is, your life is...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.60,0:13:47.91,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,Are you serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.10,0:13:49.64,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,M-Mr. Kuro, is everything cool?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.31,0:13:52.45,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, but how about over there?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.61,0:13:55.82,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,So far it's fine, but not for long, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.95,0:13:57.22,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,We should start the plan soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.75,0:14:02.29,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,If they are planning to double\Ncross us, we'll get even with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.38,0:14:05.09,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,Mr. Kuro, actually\NMikura went shopping...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.39,0:14:06.49,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,H-Harada?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.56,0:14:08.66,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,Hello, what's up Harada?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.83,0:14:14.27,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.76,0:14:16.54,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,It's the rest of the money.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.60,0:14:18.37,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,Please take it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.47,0:14:20.57,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,Why are you giving it to me now?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.80,0:14:25.68,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,I refused to pay the rest of the\Nmoney because of Momokichi's death.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.84,0:14:28.15,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,But that was childish...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.84,0:14:33.05,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,And if I give it to those two,\Nthey'll disappear before finishing the job.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.12,0:14:35.96,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,Pops and Harada won't betray me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.15,0:14:37.65,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,Is that so...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.12,0:14:41.16,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,But I'll put it in my\Nown account, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.49,0:14:47.30,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,In any case, where\Ndid you meet those two?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.36,0:14:48.74,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,A jail in the police station...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.00,0:14:51.21,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,We were busted\Nwhen Pops was a detective.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.27,0:14:52.94,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,What did you two do?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.00,0:14:56.38,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,Harada produced Androids\Nand sold them underground.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.54,0:14:57.31,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,As for me...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.27,0:14:59.27,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,Guess what I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.61,0:15:02.42,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,Found you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.48,0:15:03.46,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,Run away!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.32,0:15:10.82,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,Bitch!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.86,0:15:14.43,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,Ouch...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.52,0:15:16.43,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,Good job, bastard macho beard man!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.53,0:15:25.17,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,Take this!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.64,0:15:29.12,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,Come out, psycho bitch!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.57,0:15:31.45,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,Oh, shit...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.17,0:15:34.88,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,I want to slit your throat right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.98,0:15:38.82,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,Pops, I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.85,0:15:44.69,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,I don't look at all like this pig!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.99,0:15:51.20,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,Oh my God, is it this bad?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.53,0:15:56.31,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,Mikura!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.40,0:15:57.21,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,Harada!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.33,0:16:02.54,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,Absurdly, unbelievably bad...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.91,0:16:07.82,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,Harada...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.51,0:16:09.32,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,Mr. Kuro!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.38,0:16:12.88,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,You scared the shit out of me,\Nbut at least you're safe, Harada.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.28,0:16:16.75,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,They didn't find the\Nshelter in the basement...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.89,0:16:18.46,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,So Mikura is fine, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.52,0:16:19.97,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,Well, she was...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.19,0:16:20.89,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,Mikura was...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.56,0:16:23.90,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,...taken away by them.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.03,0:16:31.24,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,The taser knocked\Nout your nervous system.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.93,0:16:34.85,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,You can't move on your\Nown for five to six hours...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.57,0:16:40.45,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,Where did you hide my papa?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.01,0:16:42.32,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,I don't know...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.41,0:16:45.02,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,Who is Papa?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.62,0:16:48.79,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,I hate torture.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.92,0:16:52.33,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,It's primitive, savage and\Nnot particularly intellectual.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.26,0:16:55.00,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,I'll ask you one more time.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.06,0:16:56.13,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,Where is Papa?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.13,0:17:00.20,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,I-I'm hungry, let me eat something.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.76,0:17:05.44,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,You're being impudent.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.77,0:17:12.77,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,Ms. Momomi, a call from the kidnapper.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.94,0:17:14.08,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,Come to the living room!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.68,0:17:18.21,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,You're lucky, I was\Ngoing to carve up your face.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.15,0:17:21.15,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,I didn't think you'd be alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.38,0:17:23.06,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,I guess you really were a detective.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.12,0:17:23.99,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,Is Mikura safe?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.79,0:17:28.00,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,If you want her back,\Nhealthy and normal...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.56,0:17:31.50,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,I'll exchange Momokichi with Mikura.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.99,0:17:33.30,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.60,0:17:35.27,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,How about tonight\Nat the Peach stadium?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.73,0:17:36.57,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.73,0:17:38.71,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,And I have one question.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.80,0:17:40.30,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,Please be frank.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.67,0:17:43.67,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,Who were your collaborators?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.44,0:17:51.39,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,Pops, Harada...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.32,0:17:58.49,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,Thank you for waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.89,0:18:01.23,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,I'll take you to the girl's room, now...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.72,0:18:03.86,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,...think of it as a thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.30,0:18:10.61,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,Look, she's really worn out.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.00,0:18:11.67,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.77,0:18:12.71,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,Nice to see you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.84,0:18:17.84,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,They told me about your\Nconversation in the Family Restaurant.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.11,0:18:21.28,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,Because of them, I didn't have\Nto waste time looking for a pig.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.64,0:18:24.85,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,We can have the girl until\Nthe time of the deal, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.61,0:18:26.96,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,About eight hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.05,0:18:28.39,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,Use it efficiently.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.02,0:18:31.02,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,Where is Hirooka?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.12,0:18:32.93,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,He'll be back in two hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.02,0:18:36.23,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,I didn't know he needed to go\Nto the dentist like normal people.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.29,0:18:38.17,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,He actually has a sweet tooth.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.56,0:18:41.30,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.90,0:18:45.21,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,Where's you're usual strength?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.27,0:18:51.51,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,We haven't been this\Nexcited in a while, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.38,0:18:57.02,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,I won't be easily satisfied.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.68,0:18:59.35,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,Looks good...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.32,0:19:01.62,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,Oh, shit...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.62,0:19:04.19,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,I came a little bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.25,0:19:07.26,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,Fool, you should hold\Noff so you can come inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.46,0:19:10.10,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,It was nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.56,0:19:12.54,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,Please, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.30,0:19:15.28,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,I like someone...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.66,0:19:16.54,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.60,0:19:17.10,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,So what?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.57,0:19:23.52,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,The price of our anger is expensive.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.07,0:19:26.88,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,I want to hear her scream.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.31,0:19:28.34,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,No, stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.41,0:19:31.39,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,How is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.45,0:19:33.59,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,I'll push it in as deep as it goes!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.29,0:19:38.86,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,Don't come inside!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.99,0:19:43.80,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,Let me go, I can't take any more.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.86,0:19:45.27,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,Relief batter stepping up!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.93,0:19:50.90,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,This is punishment for\Nyour gun and that fork!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.97,0:19:56.54,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,She's ready for some\Nspecial time together.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.67,0:19:58.62,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,You really like it, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.68,0:20:01.05,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,No, that's too much...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.28,0:20:06.45,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,Ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.69,0:20:13.26,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey, hey-
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.42,0:20:14.46,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,Again?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.69,0:20:16.43,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,Look at this.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.69,0:20:19.50,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,Drink everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.80,0:20:28.71,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,I can't drink that much.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.77,0:20:32.01,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,If you don't listen to me, we'll\Nhave more special time together.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.14,0:20:32.98,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.04,0:20:35.18,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,It was too good and I almost came...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.24,0:20:37.99,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,I want her boyfriend to hear this.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.05,0:20:40.05,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,Then, we'll make you feel much better.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.15,0:20:41.79,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,More, more.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.85,0:20:43.45,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,Push it deeper!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.00,0:21:02.81,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,Come and get Papa Peach.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.17,0:21:05.88,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,You two, come over\Nand get the Orange Girl, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.38,0:21:07.05,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,Mr. Kuro.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.41,0:21:08.41,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.81,0:21:10.31,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,Hirooka, let them get set up.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.58,0:21:12.25,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,Then, I'll tell them.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.72,0:21:19.70,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,Are you guys TENN?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.62,0:21:21.69,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,We're ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.06,0:21:25.87,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,All right, give my regards to the Owner.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.73,0:21:29.94,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Papa.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.23,0:21:32.77,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,Although I was with you,\Nsuch a bad thing happened...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.67,0:21:36.24,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,Watch, I'll victimize them!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.47,0:21:38.61,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,Don't do anything to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.74,0:21:40.22,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,I don't like violence.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.28,0:21:41.65,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,What are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.71,0:21:43.62,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,Did you forget your Peach soul?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.85,0:21:45.29,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,You're acting strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.68,0:21:49.09,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,Two of them were so cruel to me...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.15,0:21:51.06,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,I see, I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.59,0:21:53.53,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,Harada, blow them up!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.59,0:21:54.09,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.76,0:21:57.13,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,I'll come over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.36,0:22:00.00,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,I'm waiting at the gate, hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.40,0:22:02.53,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,Papa, let's run.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.43,0:22:04.64,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,Run, run.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.70,0:22:06.20,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,Oh, let's!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.40,0:22:08.75,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,Something's not right...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.61,0:22:11.58,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.11,0:22:14.59,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,Great, now when I\Nneed it to work most!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.81,0:22:16.38,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,We're in a blind alley.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.48,0:22:17.62,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,Let's go outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.28,0:22:19.52,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,It's too dangerous here.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.61,0:22:21.46,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,Okay, hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.72,0:22:23.42,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,Harada, that's too fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.69,0:22:29.29,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,It looks all clear to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.19,0:22:32.00,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,They must have something in place.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.16,0:22:34.37,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,I don't think they'll let us leave easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.06,0:22:38.10,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,But we can't just stay here, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.20,0:22:38.94,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,Mr. Kuro.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.03,0:22:39.74,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.84,0:22:40.75,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,Wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.90,0:22:41.81,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.34,0:22:43.28,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,Let's go...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.31,0:22:48.55,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,We won't let you make it to home base.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.81,0:22:50.41,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,You guys again?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.58,0:22:51.65,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,The bottom of the ninth...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.15,0:22:54.56,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,A come-from-behind home run, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.92,0:22:56.66,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,Well, the gang's all here...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.72,0:22:57.56,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,Something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.05,0:23:01.33,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,Actually, three hit men are on stand-by.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.46,0:23:04.20,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,They should be here, but I can't wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.60,0:23:11.24,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,What a turn on!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.30,0:23:12.07,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,I can't help it...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.63,0:23:13.91,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,She is psycho...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.87,0:23:16.21,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,Go ahead, start the engine.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.47,0:23:17.58,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.91,0:23:19.51,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,No shit, it's...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.01,0:23:23.18,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,What is it, never seen a corpse before?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.65,0:23:24.49,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.58,0:23:25.35,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,This is a...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.98,0:23:29.83,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,Papa, run away!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.75,0:23:32.43,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,Bitch!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.56,0:23:35.53,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,Orange Girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.93,0:23:39.91,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,I was aiming for their heads...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.23,0:23:41.94,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,I guess my body hasn't recovered yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.33,0:23:43.43,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,You're kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.53,0:23:45.41,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,I just killed you, didn't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.70,0:23:50.68,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,An Android...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.51,0:23:53.58,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,I substituted it in\Nyour little torture room.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.22,0:24:06.37,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,How did you know about\Nthe construction of our house?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.42,0:24:08.66,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,An old friend of your Papa's told us.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.02,0:24:10.47,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,Then we did...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.76,0:24:11.83,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.39,0:24:14.17,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,You saw how efficient she was, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.33,0:24:17.04,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,She was an Android?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.37,0:24:22.15,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,Papa!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.47,0:24:23.04,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,Damn pig!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.58,0:24:29.18,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,Shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.49,0:24:40.73,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,That's why I said I\Ndon't like violence, Momomi.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.99,0:24:42.02,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,Even papa was...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.49,0:24:44.44,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,Shit...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.93,0:24:47.70,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,I lost to such a trashy bitch...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.00,0:24:51.71,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,We're scoundrels who have\Nblood and tears, understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.67,0:24:57.34,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,I'll kill you in the next world...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.24,0:25:05.85,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,She was really a psycho bitch, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.01,0:25:09.48,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,Mikura took that psycho\Ndown, for better or worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.58,0:25:11.00,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,I'm just glad she's on my side!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.05,0:25:12.26,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,I agree.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.72,0:25:15.93,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,But if this Papa\NMomokichi worked better...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.99,0:25:17.37,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,It would've saved me some trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.43,0:25:19.77,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,Well, the result is all good, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.06,0:25:25.10,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,From now on, the Peach Twister's\Nimage will be renewed.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.63,0:25:27.71,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,Everything went as you expected, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.47,0:25:30.81,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,Show us your identity.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.61,0:25:41.18,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,The pale faced man from\Nthe bowling alley.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:41.25,0:25:42.28,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,Yes, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.35,0:25:43.99,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,When did you figure it out?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.39,0:25:48.27,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,When we did a laser scan in\Nour office, we saw your frame...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.32,0:25:50.00,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,...it was not that of an old man.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.26,0:25:54.26,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,You are cunning people.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.93,0:25:57.47,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,I thought this would happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.87,0:25:59.61,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,You flatter yourself, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:00.34,0:26:01.41,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,Something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.94,0:26:05.28,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,I had to use you guys\Nas a third party to kill them.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.44,0:26:08.01,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,I'll continue their business...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.81,0:26:11.19,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,...but I'll use my own strategies.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:11.25,0:26:13.49,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,Momoi didn't know anything...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:14.15,0:26:15.99,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,...about the baseball business.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.42,0:26:19.52,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,And you guys didn't\Nknow anything about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:25.39,0:26:27.13,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.50,0:26:29.67,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,You don't know about us, either!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:30.87,0:26:31.64,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,Bingo!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:32.07,0:26:32.81,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:33.03,0:26:33.98,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,Tell me!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.47,0:26:35.64,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,Too late, that's what!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:57.39,0:26:59.17,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,It doesn't connect...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:59.36,0:27:02.43,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,What the hell is Kurokawa doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:02.53,0:27:04.81,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,The fingerprints\Ndid come through, though...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:07.57,0:27:10.21,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,We couldn't get the ransom...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:10.61,0:27:13.81,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,My car will be scraped.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:14.31,0:27:18.28,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,By the way, don't you think\Nthey'll find Momokichi's body?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:19.08,0:27:21.03,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,Even if they find it...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:21.32,0:27:23.09,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,...we didn't leave any clues.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:25.89,0:27:27.96,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,It's not game over yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:28.36,0:27:31.50,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,I told you that if I saw you again,\NI wouldn't take it easy on you!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:31.96,0:27:33.94,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,You don't have a gun, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:34.00,0:27:34.97,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,Damn bitch!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:39.47,0:27:41.85,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,Hey, it's smashed to bits.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:41.90,0:27:43.47,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,Smashed to bits...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:43.74,0:27:45.68,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,You should get a domestic car...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:45.94,0:27:47.58,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,Pops, you're on fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:57.55,0:28:00.50,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,Mr. Kuro, it'll cost a lot for the repairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:00.56,0:28:01.33,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,It's okay, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.39,0:28:03.39,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,If everybody is safe, everything is cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:03.66,0:28:04.53,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,Pops!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:05.66,0:28:07.44,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,When we will reopen our business?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:07.96,0:28:09.44,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,Not for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:09.53,0:28:10.94,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,Take care of your body.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:11.43,0:28:13.38,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,You just want to take it easy...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:15.70,0:28:17.21,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,Pops, it's another vision!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:17.27,0:28:18.77,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,Take this job, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:22.94,0:28:23.92,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,What should we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:24.21,0:28:26.21,Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,Hey, our agency\Nspecializes in dangerous jobs!
